      "iconName": "Decimation",
      "tips": "Using this ultimate in critical moments will allow your Spawn to deal legendary amounts of damage, as no hero can match the power of a full form Nightmaric Spawn. However, the crack in the planescape can only be sustained for 10 seconds, so use your time wisely.",
