    "skill1": {
      "name": "Nightmaric Spawn",
      "description": "Zhask summons a Nightmaric Spawn that inherits 55% of his Attributes (HP, Hybrid Defense, and Magic Power). Nightmaric Spawn will automatically attack nearby enemies by firing a Death Ray at the target, dealing 55 (+20% extra Attack Speed) (+20% Magic Power) Magic Damage and slowing them by up to 30%. If Zhask is too far away from Nightmaric Spawn, it will disappear.\nDeath Ray is considered as a Basic Attack but cannot Crit.\nFusion Enhanced: The damage of Nightmaric Spawn is increased to 180%, and it can be repositioned.",
      "cooldown": "13.0",
