      "iconName": "Nightmaric_Spawn",
      "tips": "Every 2 basic attacks of the Spawn will fire a death ray at the enemy. If the death ray strikes the target 7 times consecutively, then it will cause a stun effect. This is definitely Zhask's core skill, we recommend that you keep your Spawn close to you during combat, not only does this little fellow bring damage but he can also provide some extra crowd control. Also, enemies may gain quite a bit of gold slaying the Spawn, as a Planes Dominator you should always look out for the welfare of your minions.",
